<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="9Feb1938"><font color="red">9 February 1938</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Harriet Weaver): Retinal congestion &hellip; in consequence of months of day and (literally) allnight work finishing W i P. and I had to leave Paris and come here to see Prof. Vogt. All writing and reading were stopped but it was only strain &hellip; I am now allowed 2 or 3 hours a day work &hellip; I don&apos;t think I ever worked so hard even at <i>Ulysses</i> </div>
